#### Entity: ENTITIES (Index)

|  |  |  |  |  |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Attribute | Type | Required | Business Rule | Description |
| id | integer | Yes | Auto-increment | Primary key |
| entry\_id | integer | Yes | FK to knowledge\_entries | Source entry |
